  "text": "In this study, we use a combinatorial fusion technique to facilitate prediction results selection and combination for improving predictive accuracy in biological activities of inhibitors. The combinatorial fusion we take is analogous to that used in information retrieval [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , pattern recognition [CITATION_3] , molecular similarity searching and structure-based screening [CITATION_4] , and microarray gene expression analysis [CITATION_5] . These works have demonstrated the following remark [CITATION_6] .",
